WEBVTT

00:01.525 --> 00:03.315
I've been walking in my sleep.

00:03.360 --> 00:06.155
- I woke up in a drained pond.
- I was right there with you.

00:06.200 --> 00:09.780
You found a rope and a cinder block
and then you tied it to your ankle

00:09.825 --> 00:11.585
and you threw it into a goddamn lake.

00:11.630 --> 00:14.250
And if not for an act
of divine intervention,

00:14.295 --> 00:15.765
you'd be gone.

00:15.810 --> 00:17.190
Why are we losing?

00:17.235 --> 00:18.975
Because they're
giving them something.

00:19.020 --> 00:20.565
We can strip it away,
but once it's gone,

00:20.610 --> 00:23.170
we have nothing to
put back in its place.

00:23.215 --> 00:25.020
Well, let's give them something.

00:25.065 --> 00:26.855
Who wants a hug?

00:26.900 --> 00:28.610
I know you go out
there to pray with him.

00:28.655 --> 00:30.705
Do you know what your father
would do if he found out?

00:30.750 --> 00:31.985
Shoot him again?

00:32.030 --> 00:34.210
My son, Tommy, is he there with you?

00:34.255 --> 00:36.050
No, he's not here.
I've never even met him.

00:36.095 --> 00:38.200
If you do see him,
can you tell him I'm sorry?

00:38.245 --> 00:40.295
I think I just made your
sister uncomfortable.

00:40.340 --> 00:42.200
You don't make me feel uncomfortable.

00:42.245 --> 00:44.630
Have you been noticing that
I've been kind of losing my mind?

00:44.675 --> 00:46.665
I'm letting you handcuff me
to the bed every night

00:46.710 --> 00:48.255
and we're acting like
that's totally normal.

00:48.300 --> 00:50.190
I've been seeing Patti Levin.

00:50.235 --> 00:52.690
- But she's dead.
- Yeah.

00:52.735 --> 00:54.015
What is she saying?

00:54.060 --> 00:56.225
She's saying I never should
have told you about her,

00:56.270 --> 00:58.225
that I just made a big mistake.

